:backuphosts
%EchoAndLog% 正在备份原 hosts 文件...
set "bakfilename=hosts_%date%_%time:~0,8%.bak"
set bakfilename=%bakfilename:/=-%
set bakfilename=%bakfilename:\=-%
set bakfilename=%bakfilename::=-%
